  "texts": [
    "If the decision tree is trained directly based on these data, the structure of the decision tree will be extremely complex.",
    "It is difficult to achieve better classification effect and generalisation performance.Therefore, before building the early warning model, the indicators with high information content and low correlation are selected by the improved random forest analysis of the indicators.",
    "One of the key problems in constructing a random forest is to select the number of features to make it optimal.",
    "If the number of features is reduced, the correlation and classification ability of the tree is correspondingly reduced.",
    "Conversely, increasing the number of features will increase both."
